<plot>Wouldn't it be wonderful to Talk to the Animals? Well, the Kidsongs Kids can. They learn to chat in chimpanzee, giggle in guinea pig and discuss in rhinoceros, then one alligator says to another, See You Later, Alligator. Elephants and eagles, buffaloes and beagles and many, many more animal friends join the cast of this wonderful animal adventure that will keep you singing and laughing along.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?291167</url></doc>
